data.description: So adorable and affordable now available!! This renovated cozy Ranch home has many updates featuring an attractive, new vinyl plank flooring and carpeting with much more to offer. A newer roof, replacement windows, water heater, fixtures, furnace, updated tiled kitchen and bathroom along with modern paint colors throughout. The kitchen includes all the existing appliances for you as well. The perks of having everything all on one level and easy to maintain yard in a nice neighborhood close to conveniences. For a private showing and to make this lovely home your very own, Call Noelle Pelton 269-579-2319.
